@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
    ViewBag.Message = "Welcome to FitFeast&Explore!";
}
<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
    <h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

    <p>FitFeast&Explore is your all-in-one solution for managing your fitness, exploring new and exciting recipes, and planning unforgettable travel adventures. We believe in promoting a balanced lifestyle that harmonizes physical fitness, culinary exploration, and the joy of travel. Our platform is designed to cater to enthusiasts who seek to enhance their wellbeing through a comprehensive and integrated approach.</p>

    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>At FitFeast&Explore, our mission is to provide users with a versatile and user-friendly platform that combines three essential aspects of a healthy and fulfilling life:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Fitness Management:</strong> Empower users to achieve their fitness goals with personalized workout plans and easy-to-use tools for tracking progress.</li>
        <li><strong>Recipe Discovery:</strong> Inspire culinary creativity with a diverse collection of recipes, including diet-specific and travel-inspired options, complete with detailed instructions and nutritional information.</li>
        <li><strong>Tour Planning:</strong> Encourage exploration and adventure by offering tools to plan, manage, and book exciting tours and travel itineraries.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
    <p>We envision a world where people have the tools and inspiration to lead a balanced and healthy lifestyle. By integrating fitness, nutrition, and travel into one seamless platform, FitFeast&Explore aims to be the go-to resource for individuals seeking to improve their overall wellbeing and enjoy a more vibrant life.</p>

    <h3>Key Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Fitness Management System:</strong> Create, edit, and delete personalized workout plans to stay on track with your fitness goals.</li>
        <li><strong>Recipe Management System:</strong> Browse and search for recipes, view diet-specific and travel-inspired recipes, and access detailed cooking instructions and nutritional information.</li>
        <li><strong>Tours Management System:</strong> Plan and manage tours and travel itineraries, browse popular destinations, and book your next adventure.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Why Choose FitFeast&Explore?</h3>
    <p><strong>Comprehensive Approach:</strong> FitFeast&Explore offers an integrated solution that combines fitness, nutrition, and travel, making it easier for users to maintain a balanced lifestyle.</p>
    <p><strong>User-Friendly Design:</strong> Our platform is designed to be intuitive and easy to use, ensuring that users can quickly access the tools and information they need.</p>
    <p><strong>Community-Driven:</strong> We are committed to continuously improving our platform based on user feedback and contributions from our community.</p>

    <h3>Join Us on Our Journey</h3>
    <p>We invite you to join the FitFeast&Explore community and embark on a journey towards a healthier, more adventurous, and fulfilling life. Whether you’re looking to stay fit, discover new recipes, or plan your next travel adventure, FitFeast&Explore is here to support you every step of the way.</p>
</main>
